author: GameSpot
description:
Absolum is a punchy, impactful beat-'em-up with an interesting roguelike twist and tons of inventive build combinations, and that will always find new things to keep you on your toes. Go grab a friend to play in co-op and I promise you are in for a great time!

description:
Blumhouse Games Creative Lead Louise Blain breaks down the origins of the enemies of Crisol: Theater of Idols. Madrid studio Vermila were inspired by Spanish religious iconography and architecture to bring these unique foes to life.
